
---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms of Use" noIndex>
  <article class="mx-auto flex w-full max-w-3xl flex-col gap-6">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-serif font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">Terms of Use</h1>
    <section class="space-y-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">Acceptance</h2>
      <p>
        By accessing this site you agree to these terms. If you disagree with any part, please refrain from using the website.
      </p>
    </section>
    <section class="space-y-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">Use of content</h2>
      <p>
        All text, artwork, and media are © Mike Parsons unless otherwise credited. You may share short excerpts (up to 200 words) with attribution and a link back. Commercial reuse requires prior written permission.
      </p>
    </section>
    <section class="space-y-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">External links</h2>
      <p>
        Outbound links (Amazon, Royal Road, Audible, etc.) are provided for convenience. We are not responsible for the content or policies of external sites.
      </p>
    </section>
    <section class="space-y-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">Affiliate disclosure</h2>
      <p>
        Some Amazon links may include an affiliate tag. If enabled, qualifying purchases may earn a small commission without affecting your price.
      </p>
    </section>
    <section class="space-y-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">Changes</h2>
      <p>
        Terms may be updated periodically. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms.
      </p>
    </section>
    <section class="space-y-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions regarding these terms can be sent to <a class="text-emerald-600" href="mailto:contact@mparsonsauthor.com">contact@mparsonsauthor.com</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
